    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows clear signs of use, including several noticeable paint chips on the hood, a few minor door dings, and some light scuffing on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound; the engine starts reliably and the brakes are responsive, though it may eventually need routine suspension work. It is a solid, honest vehicle that offers great utility for the price.",
