    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking both reliability and comfort. It has been meticulously maintained, with a comprehensive service history ensuring the engine and transmission operate flawlessly. The interior is in excellent shape, featuring clean, tear-free upholstery and a smoke-free cabin environment. While the exterior shows some minor signs of character consistent with light, everyday use, the paint remains vibrant and the body is exceptionally straight. Equipped with recent tires and a fresh oil change, this car is mechanically sound and ready for the road. It\u2019s a dependable, well-cared-for example that performs as good as it looks.",
